#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/screw.rst:167
msgid ""
"These number buttons specify the center of the spin. When the tool is "
"called for the first time, it will copy the XYZ location (Global "
"Coordinates) of the cursor presently in the 3D View to start the "
"operation. You can specify the cursor coordinates using the Transform "
"Panel in 3D View, using shortcut :kbd:`T` to toggle the Panel, and typing"
